By far the worst Mcdonald's, (or any fast food place actually) I've ever been to. I work very close to this location, but very rarely get more than a drink from here. If you listen to the customers being helped in front of you, there is almost ALWAYS a problem with each order. They regularly run out of essential items and supplies, and their ice cream and frap machine seem to mysteriously "break" or "run out of supplies" every night about 1.5 hours before they close because they clean it and don't want to have to clean it again, or clean it closer to closing time. Over the years,I've seen them run out of buns, ice, pop, and no joke, meat patties. IF they somehow have all these things, their credit card machine will most likely be down.

The service at this location varies depending on which manager is working.  In most cases there is some equipment not working.  This leads to menu items not being available.  They have a tendency to accept cash only since debit card machines are broken.
